## 5. Verify the team is wired correctly

Run this from the project root:

```bash
source .claude/env.sh
check_toolchain && echo "toolchain OK"
echo "GH_OWNER=${GH_OWNER}, GH_REPO=${GH_REPO}, GH_PROJECT_NUMBER=${GH_PROJECT_NUMBER}"
echo "GH_PROJECT_ID=${GH_PROJECT_ID}"
ls "${SUPERPOWERS_SKILLS_DIR}" | head
```

You should see:

- `toolchain OK`
- All four printed values populated
- A list of skill directory names (`brainstorming`, `test-driven-development`, etc.)

If any line errors out, fix it before running the team — every agent depends
on these.

