## What changes vs. what stays the same

| File                              | Per-project? | Action            |
|---|---|---|
| `.claude/agents/*.md`             | No           | Copy verbatim     |
| `.claude/env.sh`                  | No           | Copy verbatim     |
| `.claude/project.env`             | **Yes**      | Edit per step 4   |
| `.claude/copilot-instructions.md` | Maybe        | Edit if standards differ |
| `.claude/templates/`              | No           | Copy verbatim     |
| `.claude/commands/`               | No           | Copy verbatim     |
| `CLAUDE.md`                       | **Yes**      | Edit per step 3   |
| `.claude/settings.local.json`     | **Yes** (machine) | Do not commit |

The dev-team is portable. The board's structure, labels, and the skills
location are the only per-project knobs.
